Python wrappers for libtheora.


Installation
------------

Download libtheora-1.0 from: http://www.theora.org/downloads/, install and set
the installation path in the Makefile. E.g. assuming you'll install to
/home/ondrej/usr, do:

wget http://downloads.xiph.org/releases/theora/libtheora-1.0.tar.bz2
tar xjf libtheora-1.0.tar.bz2
cd libtheora-1.0
./configure --prefix=/home/ondrej/usr
make
make install

and then cd to the python-theora directory and just do:

make
